# Puli engi
- ginger 
- 40% amount of ginger for tamrind 
- Put it in lukewarm water
- Chopped into small pieces 
- Sesame oil, mustard, 1/2 spoon methi
- Curry leaves 2 Green chilies to slit, turmeric, asofeda
- Put the ginger and fry to golden brown 
- Put tamrind water and boil
- Add Salt to taste
- Boil till the tamrind smell goes away 
- Add some jaggery to tone down gingers karam
